# NOTE: src/content/cases/*.md is generated by scripts/sync-cases.mjs from the
# private workshop, but it IS committed here on purpose: CI has no access to the
# workshop, so the build relies on the committed public content. Re-run
# `npm run sync` locally and commit when you promote a new case.
